{"id":381134,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":30}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"群众文化生活","column":"","genre":"","count":"376","ytitle":"","mtitle":"农村小唱","ftitle":"","authors":["杰人"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"杰人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深耕动员(黄家调)(男女合)秋耕秋种呀，指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年粮食收成好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(男)小麦、蚕豆、油菜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔菜统统要种好嘘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援建设都需要。(男女合)红旗锦标呀，要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六日六夜要搞好。(女)耕田、翻田、积肥、施"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥样样仔细勿潦草嘘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多快好省顶重要。(男女合)二连连长呀，俞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂台摆得真威风。(男)冬至节前、保证完成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地翻深、放出卫星，擂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台上面称英雄嘘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂台摆牢勿落空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下乡干部割稻歌(青年调)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起身早，天气好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天还不亮就上操，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先叫向右走，后叫跑步跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一二三四喊声高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝天气真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伲生活是“作稻”(注:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作稻即割稻)，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都往田里跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一到田里就弯下腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上动手就作稻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀声，嚓嚓叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越割越快象赛跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侬要割快，我要追得牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刀二刀三刀四刀五刀又六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向农民兄弟来学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取丰收指标高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都是英雄汉，个个都是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千斤目标要达到。"}]}